Drive-in cinemas are back. And the demand is through the roof. A drive-in launched by Ster-Kinekor in Joburg has sold out in its first three days. eNCA’s Nkosazana Dambuza reports. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Drive-in cinemas are back, and the demand is through the roof. A drive-in launched by Ster-Kinekor in Joburg has sold out in its first three days. READ: People still love movies, despite pandemic knock to cinema: expert Ster-Kinekor made this bold move after filing for business rescue at the beginning of this year because of financial woes caused by the COVID-19 pandemic. Watch the video above for more details.